'''Slyder's space shuttle''' was a small and heavily armed space vessel, owned by the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Slyder]], who kept it aboard the ''[[Star of Empire]]''. Slyder however operated mainly onboard the ''Star'', tracking and hunting down those who did illegal activities on the ship, such as [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Agent/Legends|agents]].

Despite its capabilities, it wasn't as large, fast or efficiently armed, compared to other private ships such as [[Dol Donar's yacht]]. Indeed, [[Skirmish on the Star of Empire|while hunting]] [[Jan Ors]] and her team, Slyder agreed to accompany [[Dol Donar II]] and his men on his [[Yacht/Legends|yacht]], after the Rebel vessel ''[[Truly Sorry]]''. Slyder's shuttle was left behind on the ''Star'', when Slyder perished in an explosion, and its eventual fate was unknown.

